RELEASE NOTES


	Stop spending time setting up Microsoft Outlook users on your network.
	A single line in your login script allows new users to use Microsoft
	Outlook XP, 2003 or 2007  for the first time without any wizards or setup. 
	
	IntelliAdmin Profile Generator is Designed for Microsoft Exchange Server
	and Microsoft  Outlook XP, 2003 and 2007.

	The IntelliAdmin Profile Generator works great with terminal servers,
	or those users that roam to different machines across your network.

	Add a single line to your login script, and the profile generator
	does the rest. You will never need to walk your new Microsoft Exchange
	Server users through the profile setup again.
